page.title: 15A DAY IN MY LIFE 1985.
page.content: I usually wake up about 7.50am.I get up and change then I go for my breakfast.I make my bed.Then I have breakfast and clean my teeth and wash.After I go to the shop for my playtime piece and buy a packet of crisps.My brother and I muck about until 8.55am and then wave goodbye to mum and go to school which is just a minutes walk from our house.At school we have choir,recorders and our usual work.After school I go home and put the t.v. on until 6.00pm which is childrens programme time.I have no favourite programme.Then I go and play on my bike.Lastly guides from 7.00pm to 9.00pm which involves games, crafts and easy ways of making presents.Survival is learned at guides.
